eu.davidea.flexibleadapter.items

Class AbstractExpandableHeaderItem<VH extends ExpandableViewHolder,S extends ISectionable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.davidea.flexibleadapter.items.AbstractFlexibleItem<VH>
      • eu.davidea.flexibleadapter.items.AbstractExpandableItem<VH,S>
        • eu.davidea.flexibleadapter.items.AbstractExpandableHeaderItem<VH,S>
  • Type Parameters:
    VH - ExpandableViewHolder
    S - The sub item of type ISectionable
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IExpandable<VH,S>, IFlexible<VH>, IHeader<VH>

    public abstract class AbstractExpandableHeaderItem<VH extends ExpandableViewHolder,S extends ISectionable>
extends AbstractExpandableItem<VH,S>
implements IHeader<VH>
    Generic implementation of IExpandable interface combined with IHeader interface with most useful methods to manage expandable sections with sticky headers and sub items of type ISectionable.

    This abstract class extends AbstractExpandableItem.

    Call super() in the constructor to auto-configure the section status as: shown, expanded, not selectable.
    Since:
    01/04/2016 Created
    18/06/2016 Changed signature with ExpandableViewHolder
